{"tid":1683472,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"區議會選舉最強兵法：教街坊拎盡著數！","createTime":"2019-10-30T15:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T18:04:51.000Z","uid":30862,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e42b1b4e443da6cc020f83b803982dc90590b693","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"區選作用 唔洗多講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿以善小而不為</span><br />\n<br />\n【警世】其實大家究竟明唔明區選嘅意義係乜？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1682643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1682643</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n要知道區內穩扎多年既保皇黨<br />\n係有壓倒性既資源優勢<br />\n街坊係一定受惠過佢地既福利<br />\n<br />\n今次區選企出來同佢地對撼既民主派/素人<br />\n除左一定要投票比佢地之外<br />\n仲可以利用對家資源多呢一點<br />\n捉街坊心理<br />\n<br />\n就係同佢地講<br />\n如果想日後有多d著數拎<br />\n今次保皇黨就要輸！<br />\n<br />\n佢地一定滿頭問號<br />\n要解釋比佢地知<br />\n你考完試仲會唔會溫書？你搞完野仲會唔會帶套？<br />\n保皇黨過左海就係神仙<br />\n著數凈係會選舉前先會落力比你<br />\n選舉後就理撚得你<br />\n<br />\n要keep住有著數拎<br />\n就要激起保皇黨既鬥心<br />\n所謂恨鐵不成鋼<br />\n要比佢地輸一次 比佢地知道街坊拎唔夠資源！<br />\n咩成功爭取過馬路多兩秒<br />\n多一部升降機<br />\n20$影半打證件相<br />\n加強下清潔街道<br />\n咁多位街坊 你覺得夠唔夠？<br />\n咁就想拎街坊既選票 會唔會太睇少街坊<br />\n<br />\n一句到尾<br />\n無論你親口講 吹兩句水 fb gp/tg <br />\n大家要同自己區 甚至隔離區既街坊講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想繼續拎著數<br />\n就要保皇/建制輸<br />\n唯有咁 先長拎長有</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=72beea52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：為左光復香港 盡做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：不了 冇用 散播失敗主義"},{"pid":"c9437e1c4770efe619bcfbee14e76cc13f896e02","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"6d8da40f8f9b198bc41f8a0564324450bbccd066","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"c495835e4bad736b56b27189aa88a34a3dbc0010","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:58:31.000Z","msg":"香港人<br />\n真&middot;反抗"},{"pid":"068d77b657cd86e0925f918be64c94a1b90648da","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"要盡做吖<br />\n唔係點對得住犧牲既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30a5db142d6dc039803143f9f3ce9741ecd4da7","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"盡做吖香港人"},{"pid":"ea0491c19c1aa65cad5f0e6c8320ef3c3fe1f877","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"除左好嬲好嬲 我地仲有好多野可以做"},{"pid":"f7aa1624179de15bc24fe3fd8e592efdde738af8","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"112<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vkDNLPX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvkDNLPX.jpg&h=6965d99b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ec7436594822eadd4590237fd0d508893bc6fa3","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"推上熱門比更多人去做！"},{"pid":"74ee7348a3732803d212f7cde02984b39a4610ce","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:01:47.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n唔只係一個口號"},{"pid":"007711ac566d40e095ecfdd281ac5330ce2fe198","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:02:07.000Z","msg":"區議會重要架！"},{"pid":"efe89c0950addb04a1c4a6748f3ee1458a2c9527","tid":1683472,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"打狗！<br />\n救人！"},{"pid":"2fe42c0ae24c07f777b283b